---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
import Heading from "../ui/typography/Heading.astro";
import Text from "../ui/typography/Text.astro";
import Mark from "../ui/Mark/Mark.astro";
import Surface from "../ui/Surface/Surface.astro";
import Button from "../ui/Button/Button.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us">
  <!-- ═══ HERO ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <Heading as="h1" size="xl" maxLineLength={false}>About Us</Heading>
    <Text as="p" size="lg" class="about-hero__subtitle">
      The workers of Kickstarter, organized.
    </Text>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ ORIGIN STORY ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="about-story">
    <Text as="p">
      On February 18th, 2020, Kickstarter
      employees voted to form a union, becoming the
      <Mark variant="emerald">first major tech company</Mark> in the United
      States to do so. We took this step in order to invest deeply in our
      collective future at the company we love, to create a workplace that is
      safer and more equitable for all, and to support organizing efforts across
      the tech industry and the many creative communities our work touches. We
      are proud to call ourselves members of OPEIU Local 153.
    </Text>

    <Heading as="blockquote" size="md" class="pullquote text-balance" maxLineLength={false}>
      We took this step to invest deeply in our collective future at the company
      we love.
    </Heading>

    <Text as="p">
      There is nowhere better-suited than Kickstarter to understand the elation
      of completing a successful campaign while knowing that the real work is
      still ahead. As we continue to build on the victories of our first and
      second contracts, we remain true to the values that informed our
      organizing: <Mark variant="cyan">transparency, inclusion, solidarity,
      accountability, and joy</Mark>.
    </Text>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ ORGANIZING PILLARS ═════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="pillars col-[wide]">
    <Heading as="h2" size="lg" class="pillars__heading">
      What We Organize Around
    </Heading>

    <div class="pillars__grid">
      <Surface elevation={1} class="pillars__card">
        <span class="pillars__icon-badge">
          <Icon name="tabler:scale" />
        </span>
        <Heading as="h3" size="sm" class="pillars__title">Equitable Pay</Heading>
        <Text as="p" size="sm" class="pillars__desc">
          Equitable compensation across positions, creating equal pay for equal
          work.
        </Text>
      </Surface>

      <Surface elevation={1} class="pillars__card">
        <span class="pillars__icon-badge">
          <Icon name="tabler:users-group" />
        </span>
        <Heading as="h3" size="sm" class="pillars__title">Diversity & Inclusion</Heading>
        <Text as="p" size="sm" class="pillars__desc">
          Diversity and inclusion in every aspect of the company.
        </Text>
      </Surface>

      <Surface elevation={1} class="pillars__card">
        <span class="pillars__icon-badge">
          <Icon name="tabler:clipboard-check" />
        </span>
        <Heading as="h3" size="sm" class="pillars__title">Fair Processes</Heading>
        <Text as="p" size="sm" class="pillars__desc">
          Fair, transparent, and consistently implemented processes around
          hiring, firing, professional growth, and disciplinary action.
        </Text>
      </Surface>

      <Surface elevation={1} class="pillars__card">
        <span class="pillars__icon-badge">
          <Icon name="tabler:heart-rate-monitor" />
        </span>
        <Heading as="h3" size="sm" class="pillars__title">Employee Wellness</Heading>
        <Text as="p" size="sm" class="pillars__desc">
          Policies that prioritize employee wellness, safety, and mental health.
        </Text>
      </Surface>

      <Surface elevation={1} class="pillars__card">
        <span class="pillars__icon-badge">
          <Icon name="tabler:building-community" />
        </span>
        <Heading as="h3" size="sm" class="pillars__title">Community & Culture</Heading>
        <Text as="p" size="sm" class="pillars__desc">
          The preservation of a company culture that fosters a sense of community
          and collaboration throughout the workplace.
        </Text>
      </Surface>

      <Surface elevation={1} class="pillars__card">
        <span class="pillars__icon-badge">
          <Icon name="tabler:messages" />
        </span>
        <Heading as="h3" size="sm" class="pillars__title">Worker Voice</Heading>
        <Text as="p" size="sm" class="pillars__desc">
          The proactive inclusion of employees in company-wide decisions that
          affect us all.
        </Text>
      </Surface>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ MISSION ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="about-mission">
    <Heading as="h2" size="lg">Our Mission</Heading>
    <Text as="p">
      Since its founding, Kickstarter has been a progressive, forward-thinking
      corporate player. In 2015, the company was reincorporated as a Public
      Benefit Corporation. This framework recognizes that our responsibility
      extends well beyond shareholders, committing us as a company to the
      pursuit of just, responsible, and equitable business practices. We believe
      that unionizing furthers these aims, while also allowing us to advocate
      for workers&rsquo; rights, which is an inherent aspect of fighting
      inequality. Utilizing workers&rsquo; collective power to improve our
      workplace is a natural extension of Kickstarter&rsquo;s mission,
      encouraging every employee to safeguard and enrich our charter commitments
      to creativity, equity, and a positive impact on society.
    </Text>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ CONTRACT VARIANT A: SURFACE CARD ═══════════════════════════════ -->
  <Surface elevation={1} class="contracts-card">
    <Heading as="h2" size="lg" maxLineLength={false}>Our Contracts</Heading>
    <Text as="p">
      On June 17th, 2022, our bargaining unit overwhelmingly voted YES to
      ratify our first collective bargaining agreement. In December 2025, after
      a <Mark variant="amber">historic 42-day strike</Mark>, 98% of our union
      voted to ratify a second contract with even stronger protections.
    </Text>
    <Text as="p" size="sm" class="contracts-card__thanks">
      Thank you for all of your support through both contract campaigns &mdash;
      it has meant the world to us.
    </Text>
    <div class="contracts-card__actions">
      <Button as="a" href="/contracts/2025" variant="primary">2025 Contract</Button>
      <Button as="a" href="/contracts/2022" variant="ghost">2022 Contract</Button>
    </div>
  </Surface>

</BaseLayout>

<script>
  const grid = document.querySelector('.pillars__grid');
  if (grid) {
    grid.classList.add('has-reveal');
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver(
      (entries) => {
        for (const entry of entries) {
          if (entry.isIntersecting) {
            entry.target.classList.add('is-revealed');
            observer.unobserve(entry.target);
          }
        }
      },
      { threshold: 0.8 },
    );
    grid.querySelectorAll('.pillars__card').forEach((card) => observer.observe(card));
  }
</script>

<style>
  /* ═══ HERO ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  .about-hero {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: var(--ksru-space-sm);
    margin-block: var(--ksru-space-2xl) var(--ksru-space-xl);
  }

  .about-hero > :where(h1, p) {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about-hero__subtitle {
    color: color-mix(in oklch, currentColor, transparent 30%);
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  /* ═══ ORIGIN STORY ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  .about-story {
    margin-block: 0 var(--ksru-space-2xl);
  }

  .pullquote {
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.4;
    border-inline-start: 4px solid var(--ksru-emerald-400);
    padding-inline-start: 1.25em;
    padding-block: 0.4em;
    margin-block: var(--ksru-space-sm);
    margin-inline: var(--ksru-space-md) clamp(-3rem, 5rem - 10vw, 0rem);
    color: color-mix(in oklch, currentColor, transparent 15%);
    float: inline-end;
    max-width: 50%;
  }

  .pullquote {
    border-radius: 16px;
  }

  @supports (corner-shape: squircle) {
    .pullquote {
      border-radius: 32px;
      corner-shape: squircle;
    }
  }

  @media (width < 640px) {
    .pullquote {
      float: none;
      max-width: none;
      margin-inline: 0;
      margin-block: var(--ksru-space-lg);
    }
  }

  /* ═══ ORGANIZING PILLARS ═════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  .pillars {
    margin-block: var(--ksru-space-2xl);
  }

  .pillars__heading {
    margin-bottom: var(--ksru-space-lg);
  }

  .pillars__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--ksru-space-md);
  }

  .pillars__card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--ksru-space-lg) var(--ksru-space-md);
  }

  .pillars__icon-badge {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    width: 3rem;
    height: 3rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--ksru-emerald-500);
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: var(--ksru-space-sm);
  }

  .pillars__icon-badge :global(svg) {
    width: 1.5rem;
    height: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pillars__title {
    margin-bottom: var(--ksru-space-xs);
  }

  .pillars__desc {
    text-wrap: pretty;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  /* Staggered reveal (IntersectionObserver adds .has-reveal + .is-revealed) */
  .pillars__card {
    --_delay: 0s;
    --_delay: calc((sibling-index() - 1) * 0.12s);
  }

  .pillars__grid.has-reveal .pillars__card {
    opacity: 0;
    translate: 0 2rem;
    transition: opacity 0.6s ease-out var(--_delay), translate 0.6s ease-out var(--_delay);
  }

  .pillars__grid.has-reveal .pillars__card.is-revealed {
    opacity: 1;
    translate: 0 0;
  }

  .pillars__grid.has-reveal .pillars__icon-badge {
    scale: 0;
    rotate: -180deg;
    transition: scale 0.4s ease-out calc(var(--_delay) + 0.2s),
                rotate 0.4s ease-out calc(var(--_delay) + 0.2s);
  }

  .pillars__grid.has-reveal .pillars__card.is-revealed .pillars__icon-badge {
    scale: 1;
    rotate: 0deg;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .pillars__card,
    .pillars__icon-badge {
      opacity: 1 !important;
      translate: none !important;
      scale: 1 !important;
      rotate: none !important;
      transition: none !important;
    }
  }

  @media (width < 768px) {
    .pillars__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (width < 480px) {
    .pillars__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* ═══ MISSION ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */

  .about-mission {
    margin-block: var(--ksru-space-2xl);
  }

  /* ═══ CONTRACT VARIANT A: SURFACE CARD ═══════════════════════════════ */

  .contracts-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--ksru-space-xl);
    margin-block: var(--ksru-space-2xl);
  }

  .contracts-card__thanks {
    color: color-mix(in oklch, currentColor, transparent 30%);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .contracts-card__actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--ksru-space-sm);
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: var(--ksru-space-lg);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

</style>
